@EU_Commission @Europarl_EN @EUCouncil YOU and that guy who is called president or so have NOTHING to say about the time we are living in.

It would be an idea from morrons to say goodbye to wintertime for the Northern countries. 

DO NOT DECIDE FOR EVERY COUNTRY!

@EU_Commission @JunckerEU @Bulc_EU @Transport_EU @A_WintersteinEC Great that you received 4.6m responses.
Now you let the countries do it themself. 

Don't put your big mouth in it! Since for every country it is different what would be the best. You can NOT rule Europe like it is one country.
